      "content": "idk i dont think its just hardware issues. its weird because it feels timed. like i'll be listening to a song and then i feel this sudden shift in my mood and i swear i hear this low thud or hum right at that exact moment. its not just constant noise, its like it reacts to me. is there any way software could actually be tuned to trigger stuff like that?",
